    "name": "Midwest 90: Rapid City",
    "steam_appid": 1818480,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818480/extras/b62204a73ec91e5a8dc7d08f05b89334.avif?t=1772201589\" width=468 height=82 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >概览</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以一名小镇餐馆老板的视角，体验在怪物围城下的生存挣扎。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >研究并售卖美味的怪物肉料理，壮大你的中西部餐馆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在餐馆外布置陷阱，抵御难以预测的怪物入侵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >做出艰难的经营决定——要么活下去，要么让 Rapid City 走向毁灭。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >投入一段有血有肉的深度叙事，揭开怪物背后的谜团。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了让生意活下去，你愿意做到什么程度？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获取更多更新：关注我们的 Discord 与 Facebook。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818480/extras/2499cdd73ab0b016553cc58ff5f2b49a.avif?t=1772201589\" width=468 height=105 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保卫餐馆</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818480/extras/f96d5c075e4cafc51d74fb3bee5ccb33.poster.avif?t=1772201589\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818480/extras/f96d5c075e4cafc51d74fb3bee5ccb33.webm?t=1772201589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818480/extras/f96d5c075e4cafc51d74fb3bee5ccb33.mp4?t=1772201589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在日落前武装自己、准备好员工并布置陷阱，同时让顾客和生意都活着——因为夜幕将带来什么，谁也无法预料。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818480/extras/7575e5790b5a8efb320a61ed8255fd93.avif?t=1772201589\" width=468 height=105 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >烹饪怪物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818480/extras/acb647727460ffdf272acc1740d3521f.poster.avif?t=1772201589\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818480/extras/acb647727460ffdf272acc1740d3521f.webm?t=1772201589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818480/extras/acb647727460ffdf272acc1740d3521f.mp4?t=1772201589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用怪物肉制作离奇却出奇诱人的菜肴！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同菜品会对顾客产生不同效果——如何搭配菜单，全由你决定！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但请记住：每个选择都会带来后果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818480/extras/834548b06ee5fe9bd2a4b8c20eacea5f.avif?t=1772201589\" width=468 height=105 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经营</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818480/extras/83d638b7c5fbb3332745bef41d1ba018.poster.avif?t=1772201589\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818480/extras/83d638b7c5fbb3332745bef41d1ba018.webm?t=1772201589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818480/extras/83d638b7c5fbb3332745bef41d1ba018.mp4?t=1772201589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的成功取决于你的经营抉择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你只追求利润吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还是把社区的福祉放在首位？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >归根结底，你的决定将左右你的命运——以及 Rapid City 的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818480/extras/f042adec88a02fceab3bcf342bf6b783.avif?t=1772201589\" width=468 height=105 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818480/extras/3acec4640b5e7966100a2adbe21ca869.poster.avif?t=1772201589\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818480/extras/3acec4640b5e7966100a2adbe21ca869.webm?t=1772201589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818480/extras/3acec4640b5e7966100a2adbe21ca869.mp4?t=1772201589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在美国中西部一个遭受“新大萧条”和神秘怪物入侵的小镇上，即便是一名餐馆经理也能扭转局面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在努力维持餐馆运营的同时，结识 Rapid City 的顾客与供货商，揭开怪物起源之谜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
